! Word Count Plugin

Displays a live word, character, and line count panel at the bottom of the editor.

!! Features

* Live word count
* Character count
* Line count
* Selection statistics (shows selected words/chars when text is selected)

!! Configuration

Enable/disable via Control Panel > Settings > CodeMirror > Editor > Show word count
